data.description: 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage in Spanish Springs nestled on 1/3 acres. Enjoy the serenity of the quiet neighborhood, complemented by an RV/trailer spot on the side of the house. Embrace your green thumb with raised garden beds, while your furry friends frolic in the expansive dog run. Additional storage is provided from storage shed in backyard. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your own. New HVAC and fans were installed 5 years ago. No repairs will be made by Seller. Buyer concessions welcome. Garage is in the process of being completely emptied out, was being used as a shop. This is a trust sale and preliminary title work has been completed. Please call for title company information.
